{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "hrms-api",
		"name": "HRMS API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for HRMS Backend (Single Database)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Organization",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Check Email",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/organization/check-email?email=admin@example.com",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["organization", "check-email"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "email",
									"value": "admin@example.com",
									"description": "Email address to check"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Step 1: Check if email already exists. Returns { exists: true/false }"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Register Organization",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set('registration_email', response.email);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"companyName\": \"Acme Corporation\",\n  \"fullName\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePassword123!\",\n  \"confirmPassword\": \"SecurePassword123!\",\n  \"longitude\": -74.0060,\n  \"latitude\": 40.7128,\n  \"radius\": 100,\n  \"officeAddress\": \"123 Business St, New York, NY 10001\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/organization/register",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["organization", "register"]
						},
						"description": "Step 2: Register organization. Stores data in temp table and sends OTP to email.\n\n**Fields:**\n- email: Admin email (must be unique)\n- companyName: Company name (must be unique)\n- fullName: Admin full name\n- password: Password (min 8 chars, must contain uppercase, lowercase, number)\n- confirmPassword: Must match password\n- longitude: Office longitude\n- latitude: Office latitude\n- radius: Office radius in meters\n- officeAddress: Office address\n\n**Response:** Returns message and email. Check email for OTP."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Verify OTP",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"otp\": \"123456\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/organization/verify-otp",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["organization", "verify-otp"]
						},
						"description": "Step 3: Verify OTP. Moves data from temp table to actual tables (Organization + Admin User).\n\n**Fields:**\n- email: Email used during registration\n- otp: 6-digit OTP received via email (expires in 15 minutes)\n\n**After verification:** User needs to login separately."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Authentication",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    const response = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set('access_token', response.accessToken);",
									"    pm.environment.set('user_id', response.user.id);",
									"    pm.environment.set('user_role', response.user.role);",
									"    pm.environment.set('organization_id', response.user.organizationId);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"SecurePassword123!\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Login with email and password. Returns JWT token with user info including organizationId."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Setup Password",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"token-from-email\",\n  \"password\": \"NewSecurePassword123!\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/setup-password",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "setup-password"]
						},
						"description": "Set password for employees created by admin. Token is received via email when admin creates a new user.\n\n**Fields:**\n- token: Token from password setup email (required) - uniquely identifies the user\n- password: New password (min 8 chars, must contain uppercase, lowercase, number)\n\n**Note:** Token expires in 24 hours. After setting password, user can login normally. Email is not needed as the token uniquely identifies the user."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Users",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Create User",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Jane\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Smith\",\n  \"email\": \"jane.smith@example.com\",\n  \"mobileNumber\": \"+1234567890\",\n  \"role\": \"employee\",\n  \"status\": \"active\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/user",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["user"]
						},
						"description": "Create a new user. Admin only. Password setup email will be sent.\n\n**Important:**\n- Email must be unique across all organizations\n- Role can only be 'employee' (admin role is not allowed - only one admin per organization)\n- If role is not provided, defaults to 'employee'"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Bulk Upload Users",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "formdata",
							"formdata": [
								{
									"key": "file",
									"type": "file",
									"src": [],
									"description": "Excel file with columns: First Name, Last Name, Email, Mobile Number, Role (must be 'employee'), Status. All emails must be unique."
								}
							]
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/user/bulk-upload",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["user", "bulk-upload"]
						},
						"description": "Bulk upload users from Excel file. Admin only.\n\n**Excel Format:**\n- Columns: First Name, Last Name, Email, Mobile Number, Role, Status\n- All emails must be unique across all organizations\n- Role can only be 'employee' (admin role will be rejected)\n- Invalid rows will be skipped with error messages showing row numbers"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get All Users",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/user",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["user"]
						},
						"description": "Get all users. Admin sees all users in their organization, employee sees only their own profile."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get User By ID",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/user/:id",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["user", ":id"],
							"variable": [
								{
									"key": "id",
									"value": "{{user_id}}",
									"description": "User ID"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Get user by ID. Employees can only view their own profile."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Update User",
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Jane Updated\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Smith Updated\",\n  \"email\": \"jane.updated@example.com\",\n  \"mobileNumber\": \"+1234567890\",\n  \"status\": \"active\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/user/:id",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["user", ":id"],
							"variable": [
								{
									"key": "id",
									"value": "{{user_id}}",
									"description": "User ID to update"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Update user information. Admin only.\n\n**Important:**\n- Admin user CANNOT be updated (protected)\n- Email must be unique if being updated\n- Role cannot be updated (immutable)\n- All fields are optional - only provided fields will be updated"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Delete User",
					"request": {
						"method": "DELETE",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/user/:id",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["user", ":id"],
							"variable": [
								{
									"key": "id",
									"value": "{{user_id}}",
									"description": "User ID to delete"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Delete a user. Admin only.\n\n**Important:**\n- Admin user CANNOT be deleted (protected)\n- Only employee users can be deleted"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Attendance",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Check In",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "formdata",
							"formdata": [
								{
									"key": "latitude",
									"value": "40.7128",
									"type": "text",
									"description": "User's latitude"
								},
								{
									"key": "longitude",
									"value": "-74.0060",
									"type": "text",
									"description": "User's longitude"
								},
								{
									"key": "address",
									"value": "123 Business St, New York, NY 10001",
									"type": "text",
									"description": "Optional address"
								},
								{
									"key": "selfie",
									"type": "file",
									"src": [],
									"description": "Selfie image (JPEG/PNG, max 5MB)"
								}
							]
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/attendance/check-in",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["attendance", "check-in"]
						},
						"description": "Check in with selfie and location. Uses form-data (multipart/form-data). Location must be within office radius.\n\n**Form Data Fields:**\n- latitude: Number (required) - User's latitude\n- longitude: Number (required) - User's longitude\n- address: String (optional) - Address text\n- selfie: File (required) - Selfie image (JPEG/PNG, max 5MB)\n\n**Note:** Form data sends strings, but latitude/longitude are automatically converted to numbers."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Check Out",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "formdata",
							"formdata": [
								{
									"key": "latitude",
									"value": "40.7128",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "longitude",
									"value": "-74.0060",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "address",
									"value": "123 Business St, New York, NY 10001",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "selfie",
									"type": "file",
									"src": []
								}
							]
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/attendance/check-out",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["attendance", "check-out"]
						},
						"description": "Check out with selfie and location. Uses form-data (multipart/form-data). Location must be within office radius. Must have checked in first.\n\n**Form Data Fields:**\n- latitude: Number (required) - User's latitude\n- longitude: Number (required) - User's longitude\n- address: String (optional) - Address text\n- selfie: File (required) - Selfie image (JPEG/PNG, max 5MB)\n\n**Note:** Form data sends strings, but latitude/longitude are automatically converted to numbers."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get Attendance Records",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/attendance?userId=&startDate=&endDate=",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["attendance"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "userId",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Filter by user ID (admin only). Optional."
								},
								{
									"key": "startDate",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Start date (YYYY-MM-DD). Optional."
								},
								{
									"key": "endDate",
									"value": "",
									"description": "End date (YYYY-MM-DD). Optional."
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Get attendance records. Admin can filter by userId, employees see only own records."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Dashboard",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Get Dashboard Stats",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/dashboard/stats",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["dashboard", "stats"]
						},
						"description": "Get dashboard statistics. Admin only. Returns user stats, attendance stats, and recent records."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		}
	],
